{"tid":1261973,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【驚爆】四年情玩完！范冰冰宣布同李晨分手","createTime":"2019-06-27T13:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T13:53:32.000Z","uid":244704,"like":4,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5d77ce93ea99dafa59e0afb66aaafc9a2e12758b","tid":1261973,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:02:07.000Z","msg":"驚爆！范冰冰與李晨宣布分手！「晨冰」拍拖四年，即使冰冰去年捲入逃稅風波，李晨一直不離不棄，可是二人最終未能共患難到老，冰冰今日突然宣布分手，她發文：「人的一生可能會經歷各種告别，感謝一路走來你所有的給予，支持和愛。我們不再是我們，我們依然是我們。」<br />\n<br />\n李晨隨後轉發：「從朋友到愛人，再做回朋友，情感的形式會變，但你我之間最純粹的感受不會變，彼此的信任與支持是永恒的。我們不再是我們，我們依然是我們。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190627/photo/bkn-20190627203404667-0627_00862_001_02b.jpg?20190627205740\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190627%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190627203404667-0627_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20190627205740&h=b40c76fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n范冰冰微博<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190627/photo/bkn-20190627203404667-0627_00862_001_03b.jpg?20190627205740\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190627%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190627203404667-0627_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F20190627205740&h=352913dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李晨微博<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190627/bkn-20190627203404667-0627_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190627%2Fbkn-20190627203404667-0627_00862_001.html&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=db5804fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190627/bkn-20190627203404667-0627_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"72e2e7287a2cf3d07ae9adff95c04a88b312fee3","tid":1261973,"uid":139916,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T13:02:32.000Z","msg":"關我地撚事"},{"pid":"cda5e5b91b49aee61a36